  ref: "Programming Fundamentals Guide · Part 2 · 1-starting-cpp/2-trailside/4-3-compound.md (a compound statement is enclosed in braces and groups multiple statements into one block) + Part 2 · 3-structuring-data/2-trailside/03-01-struct.md"

