correct: "Iterating MAX times prints garbage rows beyond what the user actually entered."
distractors: 
  - "MAX is faster."
  - "MAX is more thorough."
  - "desk_num is unsafe."
explanation: "desks[desk_num..MAX-1] are uninitialised. Printing them = garbage values."
